### Register an admin profile from profiles control panel 
POST http://localhost:3001/api/user/register_admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "names": "user_names",
    "surname": "user_surname",
    "email": "user_email",
    "password": "user_password",
    "role": 1
}

